===Noun===
'''percent'''

# A ratio expressed as a number out of 100.
#: ''A resolution must receive fifty-one '''percent''' of the votes to pass.''

====Usage notes====
* A percentage is often denoted by the character (%).
*: '''''50%''' denotes ''50 percent''.

